This repository is a throughline *source*: a requirements graph, not a program. It
re-expresses the OWASP Application Security Verification Standard (ASVS) as a
grounded IDD graph so consuming projects can compose it with throughline-compose.

The ASVS itself is published by the OWASP Foundation under CC BY-SA 4.0. The
requirement text reproduced here in items' `text`/`attrs.source_ref` is derived from
ASVS and remains the work of the OWASP Foundation and its contributors; this
repository claims no ownership over that content and reproduces it for
interoperability. See https://github.com/OWASP/ASVS for the authoritative source.
